《'''王冠'''》（{{lang-en|''The Crown''}}）是一部英美合作拍攝的[[傳記|傳記]][[歷史劇|歷史]][[電視影集|電視影集]]，由[[彼得·摩根|彼得·摩根]]原創與編劇，並由{{tsl|en|Left Bank Pictures|左岸影業}}為[[網飛|網飛]]製作，講述現任英國女王[[伊利沙伯二世|伊利沙伯二世]]統治時期的傳記故事。觀眾對其評價普遍正面，評論家讚譽其卡司演出、導演、劇本、攝影、製作水準以及有關伊利沙伯二世統治準確的歷史記載。

第五季將於2022年11月播出。<ref name="s5rd">{{cite news |author1=Adam B. Vary |title=‘The Crown’ Formally Announces Season 5 Premiere Date |url=https://variety.com/2021/tv/news/the-crown-season-5-premiere-date-1235074072/ |accessdate=2021-11-07 |work=Variety |archive-date=2021-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211107021208/https://variety.com/2021/tv/news/the-crown-season-5-premiere-date-1235074072/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 概述 ==

《王冠》主要講述伊丽莎白二世女王一生的事蹟。第一、二季中的女王由[[克萊兒·芙伊|克萊兒·芙伊]]飾演；第三、四季改由[[奧莉薇雅·柯爾曼|奧莉薇雅·柯爾曼]]接替；<ref name="ColmanCast">{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2017/tv/news/olivia-colman-the-crown-queen-elizabeth-season-3-1202600405/|title=Olivia Colman Joins 'The Crown' as Queen Elizabeth for Seasons 3 and 4|last=Birnbaum|first=Olivia|website=美国[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]周刊|date=October 26, 2017|accessdate=October 27, 2017|language=en|archive-date=2017-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171027001128/http://variety.com/2017/tv/news/olivia-colman-the-crown-queen-elizabeth-season-3-1202600405/|dead-url=no}}</ref>第五、六季則由[[伊美黛·史道頓|伊美黛·史道頓]]演繹。

第一季故事主軸從1947年至1955年開始講述，描繪伊丽莎白與[[菲臘親王|菲臘親王]]成婚、[[喬治六世|喬治六世]]駕崩、[[英國君主加冕禮|加冕典禮]]、[[1952年伦敦烟雾事件|倫敦霧霾事件]]、[[瑪嘉烈公主_(斯諾登伯爵夫人)|瑪嘉烈公主]]與彼得·湯森的戀情和[[邱吉爾|邱吉爾]]退休等事件。

第二季故事從1956年的[[第二次中东战争|蘇伊士運河危機]]到1963年女王第三任首相[[哈羅德·麥美倫|哈羅德·麥美倫]]在[[普羅富莫事件|普羅富莫事件]]下台為止，包含1964年[[威塞克斯伯爵爱德华王子|愛德華王子]]誕生等事件。<ref name="GoodeCast">{{cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.com/tv/downton-abbey/news/a819685/downton-abbey-matthew-goode-joins-netflix-the-crown-lord-snowdon/ |title=Downton Abbey's Matthew Goode is joining the cast of Netflix's The Crown |website=Digital Spy |first=Ian |last=Sandwell |date=January 23, 2017 |accessdate=January 25, 2017 |language=en |archive-date=2018-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180923053856/http://www.digitalspy.com/tv/downton-abbey/news/a819685/downton-abbey-matthew-goode-joins-netflix-the-crown-lord-snowdon/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>由克萊兒·芙伊飾演女王統治初期的女王。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.denofgeek.com/tv/the-crown/35847/the-crown-matt-smith-nabs-role-in-netflix-drama|title=The Crown: Matt Smith nabs role in Netflix drama|publisher=Den of Geek|date=June 19, 2015|accessdate=June 26, 2015|author=Leane, Rob|language=en|archive-date=2016-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161108145035/http://www.denofgeek.com/tv/the-crown/35847/the-crown-matt-smith-nabs-role-in-netflix-drama|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="telegraph">{{Cite journal | author = Singh, Anita | date=August 19, 2015| title = £100m Netflix Series Recreates Royal Wedding | journal = 每日电讯报 | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/theroyalfamily/11813152/100m-Netflix-series-recreates-royal-wedding.html | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322133559/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/theroyalfamily/11813152/100m-Netflix-series-recreates-royal-wedding.html | archive-date=March 22, 2016| access-date = 18 November 2016 |language=en}}</ref>

第三季包含首相[[哈羅德·威爾遜|哈羅德·威爾遜]]執政時期、<ref name="THRSeason3&4">{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/crown-season-3-all-details-far-1077716|title='The Crown' Season 3: All the Details (So Far)|last=Bentley|first=Jean|website=[[好莱坞报道|好莱坞报道]]|date=January 24, 2018|accessdate=January 24, 2018|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6wj076dsM?url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/crown-season-3-all-details-far-1077716|archivedate=January 25, 2018|deadurl=no|language=en}}</ref>[[艾伯凡礦災|艾伯凡礦災]]、<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-wales-45657560|title=Netflix's The Crown films the Aberfan disaster|publisher=BBC|date=September 26, 2018|accessdate=September 27, 2018|language=en|archive-date=2018-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180926222638/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-wales-45657560|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[阿波罗11号|阿波罗11号登月]]、<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.radiotimes.com/news/on-demand/2019-01-29/the-crown-season-3-moon-landing-apollo-11-history-netflix/|title=The Crown series 3 to include episode on Apollo 11 moon landing|publisher=英国[[广播时报|广播时报]]|author=Kimberly Bond|date=January 29, 2019|accessdate=January 31, 2019|language=en|archive-date=2019-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190201013638/https://www.radiotimes.com/news/on-demand/2019-01-29/the-crown-season-3-moon-landing-apollo-11-history-netflix/|dead-url=no}}</ref>1969年的{{tsl|en|Investiture of the Prince of Wales|威爾士親王授勳}}典禮、<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/the-crown-season-3-netflix-release-date-cast-prince-philip-olivia-colman-queen-trailer-a8511406.html|title=The Crown season 3: Netflix release date, the new cast and everything else we know so far|publisher=英国[[独立报|独立报]]|date=October 24, 2018|accessdate=December 10, 2018|language=en|archive-date=2018-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181112201231/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/the-crown-season-3-netflix-release-date-cast-pr